query:
SELECT id, name, 
  CASE 
    WHEN mapData IS NULL THEN 'NEEDS_GENERATION'
    ELSE 'HAS_DATA'
  END as status
FROM trip_routes 
WHERE tripId = 30001 
ORDER BY id;
